规则说明：
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|    rule id    |                                       V505                                      |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|   rule name   |                                   AllocaInLoop                                  |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| rule category |                                     Overflow                                    |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|   rule check  |                        循环语句中使用"alloca"导致内存溢出                       |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|    message    | The 'alloca' function is used inside the loop. This can quickly overflow stack. |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

代码示例总结：
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                               V504示例                                              |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
